      • Result

        public Result(java.lang.String text,
              java.lang.String url,
              java.lang.String source,
              int size)

        Represents a result of auto-completion.

        Parameters:
        text - the result text starting with the raw search text as passedto DomainAutoCompleteProvider.autocomplete followed by the completion text (e.g. moz => mozilla.org)
        url - the complete url (containing the protocol) as providedwhen the domain was saved. (e.g. https://mozilla.org)
        source - the source identifier of the autocomplete source
        size - total number of available autocomplete domainsin this source
